Pre-Game Insights: The United States has been one of the surprise packages of the tournament thus far and will be looking to further enhance their burgeoning reputation against a Proteas team which has won all of their games but not been particularly convincing.

South African skipper Aidan Markram is looking forward to the ‘business end’ of the tournament and is grateful that they are in the Super 8s, hoping to put a more complete game of cricket together now that they move forward to the business end of the competition.
Miscellaneous Highlights: United States captain Monank Patel expressed satisfaction at receiving recognition for their efforts over the past five years.
South Africa’s captain Aidan Markram emphasized the importance of competing hard and seeing where it gets them in the tournament.
